data.description: **Fully paid off SOLAR PANELS with full price offer!!**Assumable loan at 3.25%*NO City Taxes!*0% Down, USDA eligible!!**up to $5,000 towards closing cost with full price offer**Immaculately maintained, gorgeous 2-story  home tucked perfectly in the desirable Weston Oaks estates has everything you could ask for. This large, move-in ready 4 Bedroom stately home features HIGH ceilings, flowing natural light, open floor plan and custom upgrades throughout. Main level has separate dining room/office, open chef's kitchen overlooking a very SPACIOUS family room with 11ft ceilings! Also, HUGE Primary Bedroom w/ tray ceiling offers neutral colors, full bath with separate GARDEN tub and a generous walk-in shower, granite counters with double vanity and upgraded mirror, utility room and half bath located downstairs. Spacious kitchen includes a fabulous 9 FOOT granite island with center sink, stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar w/ separate eating area, walk-in pantry, LED recessed lighting, abundance of counter space and upgraded large 42" mocha cabinets with crown molding. A convenient utility room leading to a garage with spacious ceiling space for possible storage. Gorgeous wrought-iron baluster leads to a roomy GAME/family room upstairs, Built-in Workstation, and 3 large roomy Bedrooms. Covered patio, newer ROOF, big private backyard, a blank canvas with new sod front and back allows for ones imagination to run wild! Extra energy savings with solar panels to help keep you cool and your CPS bill as low as possible in this South Texas heat! This magnificent home is close to 1604, HWY 211, HWY 151, Shopping, UTSA, Lackland AFB and SeaWorld. Beautiful and quiet neighborhood located in NISD.
